{"tid":2035724,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一代賭王何鴻燊病逝 終年98歲","createTime":"2020-05-26T05:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T05:56:40.000Z","uid":197005,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"85e4bb6f23e8ac7569fdee2b2120aa00d33f963a","tid":2035724,"uid":197005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:49:21.000Z","msg":"叱吒港澳的「賭王」何鴻燊身家超過5000億元台幣，他一生投入澳門博弈娛樂產業逾半世紀，曾擔任中國政委，有權有勢呼風喚雨。他業大家大，和4房老婆共生育17名子女。2018年底他健康拉警報，住進香港養和醫院，並在院內度過97歲大壽，那次生日合照也是最後一次子女們上傳有他的照片。雖然其實病情傳出好轉，但他一直住在該院休養。不料昨(5月25日)又傳病危，但二房女兒何超瓊對香港《蘋果》否認。據香港《蘋果動新聞》報導，他於今天下午1點05分病逝，享耆夀98歲。"},{"pid":"40c6da4031be51949063bffd5bd441b196e0b31c","tid":2035724,"uid":197005,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:50:21.000Z","msg":"係咪要上映爭家產<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93735a749728dab12ba7d4aafc186ad69d885cb6","tid":2035724,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:51:18.000Z","msg":"係咪特登整死佢<br />\nSPIN 走聽日?"},{"pid":"cc0651d5634ef72f60b448195fae83c1dffa97d4","tid":2035724,"uid":197005,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"93735a749728dab12ba7d4aafc186ad69d885cb6","tid":2035724,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:51:18.000Z","msg":"係咪特登整死佢<br />\nSPIN 走聽日?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:52:54.000Z","msg":"我係五毛係鬼係pr公司 下面唔洗屌我thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"585ea54f24172947d60f2c3a6e68edbe09c7db36","tid":2035724,"uid":28351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:53:52.000Z","msg":"零件無晒貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c59be67f095ddfde1b3e67f78fc7c4f4f70d51","tid":2035724,"uid":142854,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:5